510
00:37:27,600 --> 00:37:29,700
I'll be fine.

511
00:37:29,700 --> 00:37:32,800
Princess Rong Le, His Majesty is going to come to the manor soon.

512
00:37:32,800 --> 00:37:35,600
It's better if we keep Princess Zhao Yun away for a while.

513
00:37:35,600 --> 00:37:38,000
She has a close relationship with Prince Li.

514
00:37:38,000 --> 00:37:39,800
I'm worried that there will be troubles.

515
00:37:39,800 --> 00:37:44,360
But I feel pity for Princess Zhao Yun because she is always alone.

516
00:37:44,360 --> 00:37:48,000
