517
00:37:48,000 --> 00:37:50,800
I have always treated her like a younger sister.

518
00:37:50,800 --> 00:37:53,400
I can't bear to see her sad.

519
00:37:55,800 --> 00:37:57,800
What is it, Princess Zhao Yun?

520
00:37:57,800 --> 00:37:59,600
It's nothing.

521
